snippet.title: SABOTAGE: A new versus mode for Orcs Must Die! Unchained!
snippet.description:
** Introducing Sabotage, the newest versus mode for Orcs Must Die! Unchained **
◄ Play now: http://www.OrcsMustDie.com ►

***********************************************************************

In Sabotage, two teams of heroes compete on separate, but identical battlegrounds to see who can defend the rift the best! Each team can disrupt their enemies match by sending additional minions and bosses and by casting powerful spells that are new to Sabotage. It takes teamwork, cunning, and a little bit of luck to keep the rift safe and the team with the most rift points at the end is the winner!

***********************************************************************

◄ Watch Orcs Must Die! Unchained LIVE: http://OMD.tv ►
